version_description:
- Completely rewritten the whole connecting system.
- No longer runs on URL, runs a pure sockets.
- UI has been updated.
- Players page can't be shown when there is more then 100 players, because of limitations in SA-MP.
- Support page has been added.
- Bug fixes that caused the application to crash on collecting server information.
